563
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:24,130
don't hold back.

564
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:27,230
As long as you're sure you are in the right direction,

565
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:28,570
just push straight through.

566
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,000
If you get stuck,

567
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:31,610
it means you're not pushing hard enough.

568
00:21:31,870 --> 00:21:33,240
Put in more effort.

569
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:35,340
No one can take you down on your own battlefield.

570
00:21:35,770 --> 00:21:36,470
Come on.

571
00:21:36,630 --> 00:21:37,430
You can definitely do it.

572
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,040
You have so much confidence in me?

573
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:42,350
Back then,

574
00:21:42,870 --> 00:21:44,360
during the group-buying war,

575
00:21:44,390 --> 00:21:45,380
you were in Xiamen.

576
00:21:45,430 --> 00:21:46,910
You realized the trend was changing,

577
00:21:46,930 --> 00:21:49,010
and you called your boss overnight,

578
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,620
telling him to shift the strategic focus

579
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:52,150
from group-buying to food delivery.

580
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,620
If it weren't for that call,

581
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:57,420
whether Bee would still exist now would be unknown.

582
00:21:58,150 --> 00:22:00,910
So your boss should be very clear

583
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:02,230
who he should support.

584
00:22:03,980 --> 00:22:04,820
Hope so.

585
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,850
Brother-in-law!

586
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:12,560
How could they do that?

587
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:14,940
I was doing well at the Haidian branch,

588
00:22:14,970 --> 00:22:17,240
and suddenly they decided to parachute someone in,

589
00:22:17,540 --> 00:22:20,160
saying it's to assist me. Do they think I'm stupid?

590
00:22:20,260 --> 00:22:21,910
What are they really up to?

591
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:26,260
You didn't do a good job yourself.

592
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:27,750
The higher-ups have concerns.

593
00:22:27,790 --> 00:22:29,300
If the higher-ups have concerns, they can bring them up to me.

594
00:22:29,330 --> 00:22:31,010
I never said I wouldn't correct my mistakes.

595
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:32,210
But now, all of a sudden,

596
00:22:32,230 --> 00:22:33,550
they sent someone to take over our territory.

597
00:22:33,580 --> 00:22:34,350
What's that supposed to mean?

598
00:22:34,490 --> 00:22:36,540
Was all our previous work for nothing?

599
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,270
Do you know anything about Xie Wanghe?

600
00:22:40,290 --> 00:22:41,850
He's just a ground promoter.

601
00:22:44,060 --> 00:22:45,310
Why should I know about him?

602
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:47,020
During the group-buying war,

603
00:22:47,050 --> 00:22:48,410
Xie Wanghe's achievements were remarkable.

604
00:22:48,940 --> 00:22:50,020
If it weren't for him,

605
00:22:51,130 --> 00:22:52,840
Bee might not even exist today.

606
00:22:53,940 --> 00:22:54,870
When dealing with someone like him,

607
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:56,690
you absolutely can't confront him head-on.

608
00:22:58,390 --> 00:22:59,310
Otherwise,

609
00:23:01,060 --> 00:23:02,410
you'll only embarrass yourself.

610
00:23:02,780 --> 00:23:03,850
According to what you're saying,

611
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:05,610
we might as well just hand over Haidian's business

612
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,950
to him and be done with it.

613
00:23:06,990 --> 00:23:08,350
Why even bother discussing it then?

614
00:23:10,330 --> 00:23:11,880
Mr. Qiu, Mr. Xie is here.

615
00:23:13,910 --> 00:23:14,710
Mr. Song.

616
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:17,720
Sorry to keep you waiting.

617
00:23:17,870 --> 00:23:19,770
It's all right. Here, let me introduce.

618
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:22,000
This is Xie Wanghe, Mr. Xie.

619
00:23:22,320 --> 00:23:23,230
This is Qiu Lin,

620
00:23:23,870 --> 00:23:25,590
head of the Haidian branch.

621
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,440
Pleased to meet you.

622
00:23:28,180 --> 00:23:29,270
What kind of tea would you like?

623
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:30,220
No need for tea.

624
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:31,210
Room temperature water is fine.

625
00:23:31,850 --> 00:23:32,680
How about bottled water?

626
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:33,430
Alright.

627
00:23:33,990 --> 00:23:34,920
Qiu Lin.

628
00:23:36,490 --> 00:23:37,490
Go get some bottled water.

629
00:23:38,630 --> 00:23:40,830
Mr. Song, we're all quite busy, so let's get straight to the point.

630
00:23:40,860 --> 00:23:42,620
Let's forget about the water, okay?

631
00:23:45,490 --> 00:23:46,530
Okay, no problem.

632
00:23:46,730 --> 00:23:48,090
I'll get to the point then.

633
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:49,000
Alright then.

634
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,470
Let's sit down and talk.

635
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:52,390
Qiu Lin.

636
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:54,140
Offer your seat to Mr. Xie.

637
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:56,700
Come on.

638
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:02,330
Mr. Xie, please.

639
00:24:07,820 --> 00:24:08,690
Mr. Song.

640
00:24:08,990 --> 00:24:09,790
Mr. Qiu.

641
00:24:11,630 --> 00:24:12,760
The headquarters is

642
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:14,840
very dissatisfied with

643
00:24:14,870 --> 00:24:15,940
the work of the Haidian branch.

644
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:18,510
Do you have any idea how fierce the competition is

645
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:19,710
in Haidian?

646
00:24:19,710 --> 00:24:21,430
Let Mr. Xie finish first.

647
00:24:22,340 --> 00:24:24,100
For the food delivery industry,

648
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:26,140
the Beijing market

649
00:24:26,710 --> 00:24:27,640
is extremely important.

650
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,620
And Haidian is the most crucial area.

651
00:24:29,930 --> 00:24:31,640
However, our current

652
00:24:31,670 --> 00:24:33,700
market share in Haidian is less than 30%.

653
00:24:33,950 --> 00:24:35,470
It has even been declining recently.

654
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:39,750
With shortage of money

655
00:24:40,930 --> 00:24:42,080
and manpower,

656
00:24:42,110 --> 00:24:43,520
under such circumstances,

657
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:46,290
the fact that we can maintain a market share

658
00:24:46,330 --> 00:24:48,670
of 30% in Haidian is already quite good.

659
00:24:49,460 --> 00:24:51,460
Everyone in the industry knows

660
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:53,010
that to compete for this market,

661
00:24:53,380 --> 00:24:55,210
every platform is offering subsidies.

662
00:24:56,250 --> 00:24:57,190
Look at Yuntu

663
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,600
and Eat Well.

664
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:01,340
They've already offered three rounds of subsidies just this year.

665
00:25:01,370 --> 00:25:02,370
What about us?

666
00:25:03,060 --> 00:25:04,540
Since the day I started working here,

667
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:06,170
we've only offered subsidies once,

668
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,570
and it wasn't even as substantial as the others.

669
00:25:09,190 --> 00:25:11,600
Under such fierce competition,

670
00:25:11,810 --> 00:25:13,460
I still managed to maintain

671
00:25:13,620 --> 00:25:15,210
the market share in Haidian

672
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:17,240
steady at 30%.

673
00:25:17,270 --> 00:25:19,170
If the head office is still not satisfied,

674
00:25:19,630 --> 00:25:20,920
I'll quit. How about that?

675
00:25:20,950 --> 00:25:21,830
Sure.

676
00:25:22,450 --> 00:25:24,040
I'll write a report to the headquarters,

677
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:25,110
and you'll just need to sign.

678
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:27,110
It's not like that, Mr. Xie.

679
00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:29,730
Qiu Lin

680
00:25:30,170 --> 00:25:31,280
is just short-tempered

681
00:25:31,310 --> 00:25:32,560
and speaks a bit harshly.

682
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:33,580
Please don't take offense.

683
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:35,350
It's fine. We're all on the same team.

684
00:25:35,380 --> 00:25:36,670
Who's on the same team with you?

685
00:25:37,390 --> 00:25:38,310
Who do you think you are?

686
00:25:40,990 --> 00:25:41,830
Qiu Lin.

687
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:43,190
Are you done yet?

688
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,710
Do you still want to work here? If not, get lost!

689
00:25:49,080 --> 00:25:49,880
Mr. Qiu.

690
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:52,710
Two years ago,

691
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:54,770
during the group-buying war,

692
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:57,270
all platforms were burning money.

693
00:25:57,320 --> 00:25:59,000
Mr. Meng wanted to do the same in the first place,

694
00:26:00,280 --> 00:26:01,540
but we didn't have enough funds.

695
00:26:01,550 --> 00:26:02,920
Financing wasn't going well either.

696
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:05,110
In the end, we were forced to

697
00:26:05,130 --> 00:26:07,130
leave Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou, and Shenzhen,

698
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:10,140
and we had to look for opportunities in second, third, and fourth-tier cities.

699
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:11,250
Fortunately,

700
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:14,710
our strategic direction and execution were on point.

701
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:16,670
In over 70 cities

702
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:18,330
and more than 1,000 sales points,

703
00:26:18,760 --> 00:26:20,630
we cooperated closely to break through.

704
00:26:20,820 --> 00:26:22,270
In the end, we successfully implemented

705
00:26:22,300 --> 00:26:24,010
the strategy of encircling the cities from the rural areas.

706
00:26:24,310 --> 00:26:26,260
Our survival in that round

707
00:26:26,710 --> 00:26:28,030
wasn't due to funding,

708
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:31,350
but our determination and courage to fight with our backs against the wall.

709
00:26:31,670 --> 00:26:32,550
Next,

710
00:26:33,230 --> 00:26:36,080
Bee will shift from group-buying to food delivery,

711
00:26:36,860 --> 00:26:38,310
focusing on local life services.

712
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:40,330
So, Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou, and Shenzhen

713
00:26:40,350 --> 00:26:42,270
are markets we must conquer.

714
00:26:43,770 --> 00:26:44,780
Before I came,

715
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:47,780
I made a pledge to Mr. Meng that

716
00:26:48,630 --> 00:26:49,710
within a year,

717
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:51,960
I will increase Bee's market share in Haidian

718
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,360
to 50%.

719
00:26:54,870 --> 00:26:55,670
50%?

720
00:26:55,690 --> 00:26:57,310
That's wishful thinking.

721
00:26:58,520 --> 00:27:00,070
If I don't reach the goal,

722
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,310
I'll resign.

723
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,840
Then you'll definitely have to resign.

724
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:07,920
However,

725
00:27:09,750 --> 00:27:12,180
I'll take the responsible parties

726
00:27:12,210 --> 00:27:13,220
with me when I go.

727
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:24,330
Dear passengers.

728
00:27:24,350 --> 00:27:26,250
For your safety and the safety of others,

729
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:30,030
please do not bring flammable, explosive, toxic, or dangerous items,

730
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:33,410
or oversized and overweight items into the station or on the train.

731
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,880
Please cooperate with the security check.

732
00:27:34,910 --> 00:27:35,430
Sir.

733
00:27:35,430 --> 00:27:36,920
Thank you for your cooperation.

734
00:27:37,570 --> 00:27:39,600
How much does a welder make per month?

735
00:27:39,830 --> 00:27:41,350
That depends on your skill level.

736
00:27:42,970 --> 00:27:43,980
I...

737
00:27:44,340 --> 00:27:46,100
I used to do car repairs,

738
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,290
and I can weld too.

739
00:27:47,770 --> 00:27:48,770
Do you have a certificate?

740
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:50,970
Certificate...

741
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:52,570
That's easy.

742
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,370
He can make one himself.

743
00:27:55,340 --> 00:27:56,440
Officer Xia.

744
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:58,110
I've already changed my line of work.

745
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,120
Are you sure?

746
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,300
I am.

747
00:28:01,330 --> 00:28:02,890
Prison food isn't good.

748
00:28:02,910 --> 00:28:03,770
I've got the munchies.

749
00:28:04,050 --> 00:28:05,380
A bowl of noodles would suffice.

750
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,390
Everything in Beijing is good,

751
00:28:16,780 --> 00:28:17,980
but not the noodles.

752
00:28:18,290 --> 00:28:19,610
Then why do you seem to enjoy them?

753
00:28:20,190 --> 00:28:21,300
Where are you from again?

754
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:23,200
I'm from Honghuai, Jiangsu Province.

755
00:28:23,790 --> 00:28:25,430
It's a small city by the canal.

756
00:28:26,450 --> 00:28:27,760
How long have you been in Beijing?

757
00:28:27,870 --> 00:28:29,280
I came here in 2008. You know that.

758
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,300
Did you come by yourself?

759
00:28:31,490 --> 00:28:33,520
With those buddies. We came together.

760
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:33,990
Yeah, right.

761
00:28:34,010 --> 00:28:34,970
Where are they now?

762
00:28:36,360 --> 00:28:37,530
Officer Xia.

763
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:39,900
Are you taking a census?

764
00:28:39,940 --> 00:28:41,700
For someone like you who disrupts social stability,

765
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:43,600
it's necessary to check thoroughly. No problem with that.

766
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:48,140
I've done legitimate businesses before.

767
00:28:48,580 --> 00:28:50,660
But they all failed, didn't they? I've already confessed.

768
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:53,440
Then do you know

769
00:28:53,470 --> 00:28:54,500
why you failed?

770
00:28:54,530 --> 00:28:55,750
I was just unlucky.

771
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:58,750
It's so hard to make a living without a diploma nowadays.

772
00:29:01,820 --> 00:29:03,150
How much can you really make,

773
00:29:03,630 --> 00:29:04,790
selling fake IDs?

774
00:29:05,790 --> 00:29:07,610
If you hadn't caught me, I'd be making quite a bit.

775
00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:09,520
I could make tens of thousands a month.

776
00:29:10,730 --> 00:29:11,610
Then why don't you sell drugs?

777
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:12,740
That makes even more money.

778
00:29:14,710 --> 00:29:17,030
Hey, Officer Xia, what do you mean by that?

779
00:29:17,670 --> 00:29:19,030
Even if I had the desire, I don't have the guts.

780
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:20,670
You shouldn't even have that desire.

781
00:29:21,870 --> 00:29:23,400
Work hard and honestly in Beijing,

782
00:29:23,430 --> 00:29:24,840
and opportunities will come your way.

783
00:29:28,020 --> 00:29:29,720
What opportunities could someone like me have?

784
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,370
Do you know

785
00:29:37,470 --> 00:29:38,660
how much a food delivery rider

786
00:29:38,910 --> 00:29:40,000
makes in a month?

787
00:29:41,770 --> 00:29:42,750
How much?

788
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:45,220
I didn't know before, but I've asked around.

789
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,670
When business is good, they can make 7,000 to 8,000 yuan a month.

790
00:29:46,670 --> 00:29:47,830
It's even possible to make over ten thousand.

791
00:29:48,130 --> 00:29:49,180
Really?

792
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:50,050
Of course.

793
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:51,300
But it's hard work.

794
00:29:51,340 --> 00:29:52,780
Especially when the weather is bad.

795
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:54,820
Even when there's strong wind, heavy rain, or heavy snow,

796
00:29:55,020 --> 00:29:56,310
they still have to work day and night.

797
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:58,760
When they get busy, they don't even have time to go to the toilet.

798
00:29:59,090 --> 00:30:01,150
Isn't that what we're out here for? To make money?

799
00:30:01,150 --> 00:30:02,590
Who's afraid of hard work?

800
00:30:03,530 --> 00:30:04,460
Are you interested?

801
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:06,820
If you're interested, I can hook you up.

802
00:30:06,850 --> 00:30:08,750
There's a food delivery station in our area.

803
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:09,900
Mentioning my name will help.

804
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,280
Xingchi.

805
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:14,230
Well, I've looked into your background.

806
00:30:14,410 --> 00:30:17,120
You have records of acts of bravery from both last year and the year before.

807
00:30:17,450 --> 00:30:18,980
You're quite a righteous guy.

808
00:30:19,010 --> 00:30:20,050
Your heart's also in the right place.

809
00:30:21,490 --> 00:30:23,310
Don't ever go down a path of no return.

810
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,000
Alright, eat up.

811
00:30:27,770 --> 00:30:28,950
Don't just sit there.

812
00:30:36,310 --> 00:30:37,550
Here, bubble tea.

813
00:30:37,810 --> 00:30:38,650
What about yours?

814
00:30:39,550 --> 00:30:40,990
Jiang Xiaohui, Zhou Haikuo.

815
00:30:41,010 --> 00:30:42,210
Visiting each other during work hours.

816
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,310
Each of you will be deducted three points.

817
00:30:43,830 --> 00:30:45,380
I'm... I'm sorry, team leader.

818
00:30:45,410 --> 00:30:47,010
I was just delivering bubble tea to him.

819
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:48,040
I'll get back to work right away.

820
00:30:48,060 --> 00:30:49,180
Don't just say sorry.

821
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:50,660
Is it fun to keep doing this?

822
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:52,040
I know you two are close,

823
00:30:52,070 --> 00:30:53,760
but you can't be lovey-dovey all day.

824
00:30:53,780 --> 00:30:55,030
This is a workplace.

825
00:30:55,100 --> 00:30:56,000
If you want to date,

826
00:30:56,020 --> 00:30:56,870
there's a park downstairs.

827
00:30:56,990 --> 00:30:57,390
Why don't you go there?

828
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:59,080
Is this any of your business?

829
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,880
What does it have to do with you?

830
00:31:00,900 --> 00:31:02,570
You said it yourself that this is a workplace.

831
00:31:02,670 --> 00:31:03,870
It's not a prison.

832
00:31:03,890 --> 00:31:05,560
We're not convicts.

833
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,390
What's with your attitude?

834
00:31:07,420 --> 00:31:08,630
Openly violating company rules.

835
00:31:08,630 --> 00:31:09,990
Zhou Haikuo, you think you're in the right?

836
00:31:09,990 --> 00:31:11,640
What? What's wrong with my attitude?

837
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:13,150
You're acting like you've got some special authority.

838
00:31:13,170 --> 00:31:14,440
